predictions - Variable in class dag.Vertex
 
prepare(List<Amr>, MaxentTagger, boolean) - Static method in class dag.Amr
Prepares a list of AMR graphs for either training or testing by calling either Amr.prepareForTraining(MaxentTagger) or Amr.prepareForTesting(MaxentTagger).
prepareForTesting(MaxentTagger) - Method in class dag.Amr
Prepares an AMR graph for training by doing the following: Assign POS tags to the vertices of the AMR graph that are not PropBank framesets Convert the AMR graph to a tree by applying DELETE-REENTRANCE transitions (see DirectedGraph.convertToTree()) Merge named entities into a single entity (see Amr.mergeNameEntities(Vertex)) Merge verbalized concepts into a single entity (see Amr.deverbalize(Vertex)) Remove :wiki edges from the AMR graph (see Vertex.removeWikiTags()) Annotate each vertex with its mode (see Amr.annotateModes(Vertex))
prepareForTraining(MaxentTagger) - Method in class dag.Amr
Prepares an AMR graph for training by doing the following: Assign POS tags to the reference realization and the vertices of the AMR graph Refine the given alignments through several handwritten rules Convert the AMR graph to a tree by applying DELETE-REENTRANCE transitions (see DirectedGraph.convertToTree()) Merge named entities into a single entity (see Amr.mergeNameEntities(Vertex)) Merge verbalized concepts into a single entity (see Amr.deverbalize(Vertex)) Remove :wiki edges from the AMR graph (see Vertex.removeWikiTags()) Annotate each vertex with its mode (see Amr.annotateModes(Vertex)) Calculate the span of each vertex contained within the AMR graph (see Amr.calculateSpan())
